    slug: "fed-s-jefferson-speech-how-economic-outlook-energy-effects-impact-your-mortgage-",
    title: "Fed’s Jefferson Speech: How Economic Outlook & Energy Effects Impact Your Mortgage Affordability",
    description: "Fed Governor Jefferson’s speech on economic outlook and energy effects. Learn how it affects your mortgage planning and use QFINHUB calculators to stay ahead.",
    category: "mortgage",
