    title: "Stock Market Week Ahead: Nvidia, Alphabet Earnings & Atlanta Fed – How to Protect Your Mortgage and Savings Goals",
    description: "Nvidia and Alphabet earnings, plus the Atlanta Fed's GDPNow, could shake markets. Learn how to protect your mortgage affordability and savings goals with QFINHUB calculators.",
